üî• 3 bedroom Villa Coco (120 m¬≤ living space) 

Stunning villa located near Lamai (2 km about 2 minutes drive), within walking distance to the beach (about 350 m), family market and restaurants, cafes (about 300 m).

Grandfather Grandmother Rock, Wat Ratchathammaran Temple and Hua Thanon Fish Market are in a short distance.
There is a private car park at the entrance to the property.

When you enter the massive wooden door, you are greeted by a landscaped path (280 m¬≤) leading directly to a Japanese stone garden (easy to maintain) and a 7 * 3 meter pool with a waterfall.
From the covered terrace you have direct access to the pool and large open plan living / kitchen area.
Two flat screen TVs and a fully equipped kitchen.

Three en-suite bedrooms, two on the ground floor. They are of a decent size.
On the ground floor there is a third bedroom with a flat-screen TV and a bathroom.

The property was completed in September 2015 and new renovation in 2021.
The villa is fully furnished, with air conditioning, built-in kitchen and free furniture.
